1 Sec. 7. Sections 6 and 9 of this act become operative on January 1,
2 2027. The other sections of this act become operative on their effective
3 date.
4 Sec. 8. Original sections 23-1717 and 23-1719, Reissue Revised
5 Statutes of Nebraska, and sections 23-1701, 23-1701.01, and 32-604,
6 Revised Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2024, are repealed.
7 Sec. 9. Original section 81-1414.07, Reissue Revised Statutes of
8 Nebraska, is repealed.
